A traffic police officer comes to the battalion commander and says:
- Comrade Colonel, I have a son.
The Colonel says:
- Congratulations, here's a bonus for you, 1,000 rubles.
Employee:
- Well, Comrade Colonel... The firstborn is...
a colonel.
- Okay, the bonus is 5,000 rubles.
Employee:
- Well, Comrade Colonel... the firstborn, the future thunderstorm of all violators...
Colonel:
- You're annoying me... Fuck you, take the "No stopping" sign, install it wherever you want!
